[Description]
A structure for saving the state of the graphics system.

[Explanation]
SCR_STATE is a structure used for saving the state of the graphics system, used in
the commands <A HREF="$$LINK(SaveScrState)">SaveScrState</A> and
<A HREF="$$LINK(RestoreScrState)">RestoreScrState</A>.
